snippet.title: Uncharted Fight for Fortune Trailer
snippet.description:
Uncharted Fight for Fortune Trailer. Join us on Facebook & Twitter http://facebook.com/GameNewsOfficial & http://twitter.com/gamenewstrailer. Expand Uncharted Golden Abyss with a brand new car game called Uncharted Fight for Fortune ! Power-up your cards with Golden Abyss collectibles. Play with your favorite characters (Nathan Drake, Elena Fisher and more !), discover lost treasures and artifacts, expand your experience with DLC

Uncharted Fight for Fortune Trailer. Release date : Coming soon exclusively on PS Vita ! Subscribe now to get the latest game teasers, gameplay trailers, videogame walkthrough and ingame videos !
